ARTISTIC STATEMENT:

This is a harrowing curse, polluting where it reaches, cancer, miasma of dark abyss that drains the life of the ones that it reaches, the eternal void that call our name death's journal and it travel to make the world end.
The profound thought in bringing the dark star closer to us, the rebellion put to the extreme, fatigue and imprecations join into poison, red like thickest blood, oh my mouth over flows of it , at the white beaches of the tomorrow that few witness.
Angel of discord, the rotten fruit declares this code in human syntaxis unchangeable, anyone that changes words into this code will be mark with a blessing so strong that ill be turned into a curse, a forever rabbit hole, a dark cage where you only falling, the very same theme of the code will possess you , as you will never escape the terrors and the horrors into the heart of darkness, eternal discomfort and the pain that remember us that we are alive.
The great wrong that keep us balance, haunting you because you are alive , the rabid and wrath, the pure hate and love grip you till cant hold enough, crying hoping maybe now something mean something 

Maledictum perpetuum, et finis mundi appropinquat.
